This extension works on dating sites, such as: Prime Date, Svadba, Dating.com etc. It simplifies sending invitations to chat and letters and solves 5 major problems:

- Automate the sending of messages. Just create a template and the extension will find men and send a message to each.
- Save chat history. Usually dating sites do not keep such data.
- Qualitatively notify you about a new chat or message from a man.
- Collect statistics of usage, see the performance of working on dating site.
- Work with multiple accounts at once.

Main advantages:
- The interface of all plugins is unified and is embedded in separate window;
- A wide search criteria (VIP, presence of photo, country), and source of men (online, contact list, search, your own collection);
- Notifications of new chats with sound, pop-ups and animations;
- Adjusting  sound notifications for events (new chat, new message, end of sending);
- Text templates: support for variables and synonyms;
- Integration services of automatic captcha solving;
- Sending multiple messages with specific delay;
- Automatic responses to new chats, profile views, online appearance;
- Almost unlimited storage for statistic of usage and chat history;
- Additional facilities on sites: faster login and built-in translator.

Video tutorials are available on the site. https://sender.services/en/video
